233
00:13:05.285 --> 00:13:09.830
But going back a bit. May last year.
What's that? Ten months?

234
00:13:09.831 --> 00:13:11.791
Freight lorry coming east
out of Harwich Docks

235
00:13:11.792 --> 00:13:13.835
