county in lowland Scotland.

238
00:13:21.343 --> 00:13:22.969
Seven fire starters for Lanarkshire.

239
00:13:22.970 --> 00:13:25.763
Right. Now. Detonators. spare parts.
so what?

240
00:13:25.764 --> 00:13:27.140
But we...

241
